<head>Married.</head> 
<div4 type="wed" n="1" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="30" /> In <placeName reg="Henrico, Virginia" key="tgn,1002467" authname="tgn,1002467">Henrico county</placeName>, on the <dateStruct value="--15" full="yes" authname="---15"><day reg="15" full="yes">15th instant</day></dateStruct>, by <persName n="Norwood,Reverend,William,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00013" reg="default:Norwood,William,,," authname="norwood,william"><roleName n="Reverend" full="yes">the Rev.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">William</foreName> <surname full="yes">Norwood</surname></persName>, <persName n="Andrews,Mister,A.,J.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00014" reg="default:Andrews,A.,J.,," authname="andrews,a.,j."><roleName n="Mister" full="yes">Mr.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">A.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">J.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Andrews</surname></persName>, of <placeName reg="Gloucester, Virginia, United States" key="tgn,1002411" authname="tgn,1002411">Gloucester county</placeName>, to <persName n="Parkinson,Miss,Nannie,Christian,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00015" reg="default:Parkinson,Nannie,Christian,," authname="parkinson,nannie,christian"><roleName n="Miss" full="yes">Miss.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">Nannie</foreName> <foreName full="yes">Christian</foreName> <surname full="yes">Parkinson</surname></persName>. </p> </div4> 
<div4 type="wed" n="2" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="31" /> At <placeName reg="St. John's Church">St. John's Church</placeName>, <placeName reg="Richmond, Richmond, Virginia" key="tgn,7013964" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond, Virginia</placeName>, by <persName n="Platte,Reverend,William,H.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00016" reg="default:Platte,William,H.,," authname="platte,william,h."><roleName n="Reverend" full="yes">the Rev.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">William</foreName> <foreName full="yes">H.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Platte</surname></persName>, of <placeName reg="Petersburg, Petersburg, Virginia" key="tgn,7014404" authname="tgn,7014404">Petersburg</placeName>, on <dateStruct full="yes"><day type="name" full="yes">Wednesday</day></dateStruct> <time>evening</time>, <dateStruct value="1864-12-14" full="yes" authname="1864-12-14"><month reg="12" full="yes">December</month> <day reg="14" full="yes">14</day>, <year reg="1864" full="yes">1864</year></dateStruct>, at <time value="3oclock">3 o'clock</time>, <persName n="Christian,,William,H.,T.," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00017" reg="default:Christian,William,H.,T.," authname="christian,william,h.,t."><foreName full="yes">William</foreName> <foreName full="yes">H.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">T.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Christian</surname></persName>, of <placeName reg="Williamsburg, Williamsburg, Virginia" key="tgn,7014629" authname="tgn,7014629">Williamsburg, Virginia</placeName>, to <rs type="role2">Miss</rs>.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="32" /><persName><foreName full="yes">Jennie</foreName></persName> S., daughter of <persName n="Gilliam,Colonel,J.,S.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00018" reg="default:Gilliam,J.,S.,," authname="gilliam,j.,s."><roleName n="Colonel" full="yes">Colonel</roleName> <foreName full="yes">J.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">S.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Gilliam</surname></persName>, of <placeName reg="Chesterfield, Virginia, United States" key="tgn,1002267" authname="tgn,1002267">Chesterfield county, Virginia</placeName>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="33" /> <placeName reg="Mobile, Mobile, Alabama" key="tgn,7017444" authname="tgn,7017444">Mobile</placeName> and <placeName reg="Norfolk, Norfolk, Virginia" key="tgn,7014231" authname="tgn,7014231">Norfolk</placeName> papers please copy. </p> </div4> </div3> 
<div3 type="death" n="2" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>Died.</head> 
<div4 type="obit" n="1" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="34" /> Killed, on the <dateStruct value="-07-30" full="yes" authname="--07-30"><day reg="30" full="yes">30th</day> of <month reg="07" full="yes">July</month></dateStruct>, <persName n="Wright,Captain,David,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00019" reg="default:Wright,David,,," authname="wright,david"><roleName n="Captain" full="yes">Captain</roleName> <foreName full="yes">David</foreName> <surname full="yes">Wright</surname></persName>, <orgName type="company" n="Company H">company H</orgName>. <orgName type="regiment" key="VA6">Sixth Virginia</orgName>, <persName n="Mahone,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00020" reg="mostcommon:Mahone,nomatch:0" authname="mahone"><surname full="yes">Mahone</surname></persName>'s old brigade. </p> </div4> 
<div4 type="obit" n="2" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="35" /> In announcing the death of this truly good and noble young man, I must pay a tribute to his memory.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="36" />Brave, brief and glorious was his career.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="37" />May he rest in peace. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="38" /> His remains having just been brought to the city, his funeral will take place from <persName n="Hoge,Doctor,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00021" reg="mostcommon:Hoge,nomatch:0" authname="hoge"><roleName n="Doctor" full="yes">Dr.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Hoge</surname></persName>'s Church on <dateStruct full="yes"><day type="name" full="yes">Sunday</day></dateStruct> <time>Evening</time> at <time value="3oclock">3 o'clock</time>. His friends and acquaintances, and if any of the members of his company are in the city, they are respectfully invited to attend. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="39" /> <placeName reg="Norfolk, Norfolk, Virginia" key="tgn,7014231" authname="tgn,7014231">Norfolk</placeName> papers please copy. </p> <closer> <signed>A. W.</signed> </closer> </div4> 
<div4 type="obit" n="3" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="40" /> On the <dateStruct value="--16" full="yes" authname="---16"><day reg="16" full="yes">16th instant</day></dateStruct>, of consumption, Belvidere Mayse, eldest daughter of <persName n="English,,Joseph,J.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00022" reg="default:English,Joseph,J.,," authname="english,joseph,j."><foreName full="yes">Joseph</foreName> <foreName full="yes">J.</foreName> <surname full="yes">English</surname></persName>, in the <num value="17" type="ordinal">seventeenth</num> year of her age. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="41" /> The friends of the family are respectfully invited to attend her funeral this (<dateStruct full="yes"><day type="name" full="yes">Saturday</day></dateStruct>) Afternoon at <time value="2.5oclock">2½ o'clock</time> from <placeName reg="Union, Union, South Carolina" key="tgn,2096848" authname="tgn,2096848">Union Station</placeName> <orgName n="Methodist Church" type="church">Methodist Church</orgName>. </p> </div4> 
<div4 type="obit" n="4" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="42" /> At the residence of her father, on <address><street n="Venable street">Venable street</street></address>, <placeName key="possibilities=53" n="1.000 10" reg="," authname="possibilities=53">Union Hill</placeName>, <persName n="Virginia,,Mary,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00023" reg="default:Virginia,Mary,,," authname="virginia,mary"><foreName full="yes">Mary</foreName> <surname full="yes">Virginia</surname></persName>, only daughter of <persName><foreName full="yes">Nathaniel</foreName></persName> S. and <persName n="Walker,,Mary,J.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00024" reg="default:Walker,Mary,J.,," authname="walker,mary,j."><foreName full="yes">Mary</foreName> <foreName full="yes">J.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Walker</surname></persName>, aged <measure n="7months" type="date">seven months</measure>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="43" /> The funeral will take place this Morning at <time value="11oclock">11 o'clock</time> at the residence of her father. </p> </div4> </div3> </div2> 
