<div2 type="military" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<div3 type="orders" n="1" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head><hi rend="italics"><orgName n="Navy Department" type="department">Navy Department</orgName>,<lb />office special Service,<lb /><placeName reg="Richmond, Richmond, Virginia" key="tgn,7013964" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond, Va.</placeName>,</hi> <dateStruct value="1864-09-19" full="yes" authname="1864-09-19"><month reg="09" full="yes">September</month> <day reg="19" full="yes">19</day>, <year reg="1864" full="yes">1864</year></dateStruct>.</head> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="168" />Notice.--From and after Monday Next, the <dateStruct value="--26" full="yes" authname="---26"><day reg="26" full="yes">26th instant</day></dateStruct>, the <term type="ship">Steamer</term> <rs type="ship">Shrapnel</rs> will leave the wharf at <placeName key="tgn,2625188" n="1.000 10" reg="Rocketts, Henrico, Virginia" authname="tgn,2625188">Rocketts</placeName> for the <orgName n="James River Squadron" type="squadron">James river Squadron</orgName> daily at <time value="7am">7 o'clock A. M.</time> and <time value="3pm">3 o'clock P. M.</time>, touching at all the principal landing on the river. </p> <closer> <signed><persName n="Parker,,John,H.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00094" reg="default:Parker,John,H.,," authname="parker,john,h."><foreName full="yes">John</foreName> <foreName full="yes">H.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Parker</surname></persName>,</signed> <lb /> <rs type="role2">Lieutenant</rs> in charge. </closer> </div3> </div2> 
