<milestone unit="sentence" n="227" /> --I will offer for sale, at the <placeName reg="State Court-House">State Court-House</placeName>, in <placeName key="tgn,7013964" n="1.000 5" reg="richmond, richmond, virginia" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond</placeName>, on <date>Tuesday</date>, the <dateStruct value="1864-12-20" full="yes" authname="1864-12-20"><day reg="20" full="yes">20th</day> of <month reg="12" full="yes">December</month>, <year full="yes">1864</year>,</dateStruct> as administrator on the estate of <persName n="Suddith,Mrs.,Kate,J.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00124" reg="default:Suddith,Kate,J.,," authname="suddith,kate,j."><roleName n="Mrs." full="yes">Mrs.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">Kate</foreName> <foreName full="yes">J.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Suddith</surname></persName>, a Negro Woman named <persName><foreName full="yes">Bettie</foreName></persName>, <measure n="25years" type="date">twenty-five years</measure> old, to satisfy claims against the estate.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="228" />Sale to be at <time value="12oclock">12 o'clock</time>. <persName n="Pilkinton,,Richard,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00125" reg="default:Pilkinton,Richard,,," authname="pilkinton,richard"><foreName full="yes">Richard</foreName> <surname full="yes">Pilkinton</surname></persName>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="229" /> All persons having claims against the estate will please present them to me. </p> <closer> <signed><persName n="Pilkinton,,E.,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00126" reg="default:Pilkinton,E.,,," authname="pilkinton,e."><foreName full="yes">E.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Pilkinton</surname></persName>, Administrator.</signed> <term type="printrun">de 10--10t*</term> </closer> </div3> </div2> 
